  "texts": [
    "The findings aim to enhance the understanding of PL as delivered by a tutor bot based on current technological capabilities.",
    "The tutor bot demonstrated its effectiveness in accommodating learners with a range of expression and cognitive abilities.",
    "Through interactive conversations centered on PL objectives, the tutor bot successfully assisted learners in identifying and addressing their individual knowledge gaps, providing tailored guidance and support.",
    "This personalized approach aligns with the foundational levels of our PL framework, enabling learners to receive targeted assistance throughout their learning experience.",
    "The results of our experiment indicated that the tutor bot significantly enhanced learners' knowledge and understanding of the content."
